div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-solrclient.optimize-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">maxSegments</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       Optimizes down to at most this number of segments. Since Solr 1.3      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">softCommit</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       This will refresh the 'view' of the index in a more performant manner, but without "on-disk" guarantees. (Solr4.0+)      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">waitSearcher</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       Block until a new searcher is opened and registered as the main query searcher, making the changes visible.       </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-solrclient.optimize-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns a SolrUpdateResponse on success or throws an exception on failure.  </p> </div>  <div class="refsect1 errors" id="refsect1-solrclient.optimize-errors">  <h3 class="title">错误／异常</h3>  <p class="para">   Throws <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.solrclientexception.php" class="classname">SolrClientException</a></span> if the client had failed, or there was a connection issue.  </p>  <p class="para">   Throws <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.solrserverexception.php" class="classname">SolrServerException</a></span> if the Solr Server had failed to process the request.  </p> </div>  <div class="refsect1 notes" id="refsect1-solrclient.optimize-notes">  <h3 class="title">注释</h3>  <div class="warning"><strong class="warning">警告</strong>   <p class="para">    PECL Solr &gt;= 2.0 only supports Solr Server &gt;= 4.0    </p>   <p class="para">    Prior to PECL Solr 2.0 this method used to accept these arguments "int \$maxSegments, bool \$waitFlush, bool \$waitSearcher".   </p>  </div> </div>  <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-solrclient.optimize-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link SolrClient::commit()} - Finalizes all add/deletes made to the index</span></li>    <li><span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832">{@link SolrClient::rollback()} - Rollbacks all add/deletes made to the index since the last commit</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
